bio:
Freja lives and works at the Divine Elegance store. This store is located in the Reach, on the outskirts of Old Hroldan near the banks of the Karth River. Freja's coworkers/coinhabitants at the store are a man named Loki and a woman named Saga. Their high-class store sells all manner of attire for men and women alike, such as dresses, coats, hates, jewelry, and multiple other accessories. They even sell some weapons and armor, though Freja doesn't handle such deals. She is a tailor by trade.
Freja has blue eyes and long stylized blonde hair. She usually wears fancy stylish clothing, complete with opulent jewelry accessories.
name: Freja
